Package: canpumf
Type: Package
Title: Parse StatCan PUMF files
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jens", "von Bergmann", email = "jens@mountainmath.ca", role = c("cre"))
    )
Maintainer: Jens von Bergmann <jens@mountainmath.ca>
Description: Facilitate working with StatCan Public Use Microdata Files (PUMF)
    Parses the SPSS Command Files or other metadata to infer the layout structure, variable labels and value labels as well as missing data values and retun a connection to a DuckDB database with the processed data.
